IniGetMacro
===========

Allows the ``wiki`` author to insert the value of a trac.ini configuration option into a page.

Useful for ``WikiStart`` project templates.

Installation
============

python setup.py bdist_egg
cp dist/*.egg /trac/env/Project/plugins

Configuration
=============

Enable the macro in:

/trac/env/Project/conf/trac.ini:

    [components]
    inigetmacro.* = enabled

Example
=======

    = Welcome to the [[IniGet(project.name)]] Project =

